00:08:32.039 --> 00:08:33.030
that are great, right?

00:08:33.030 --> 00:08:34.940
That are very viral,
that people share.

00:08:34.940 --> 00:08:36.320
But that doesn't explain
why some are

00:08:36.320 --> 00:08:37.720
shared and others aren't.

00:08:37.720 --> 00:08:40.299
And it doesn't tell us anything
about non-cat videos,

00:08:40.299 --> 00:08:42.120
most other things that's
shared on the web.

00:08:42.120 --> 00:08:43.830
So I'm actually going to put
an X unfortunately through

00:08:43.830 --> 00:08:46.250
this cute picture of a cat
