00:09:48.720 --> 00:09:50.080
That's what everyone
wants to know.

00:09:50.080 --> 00:09:52.430
But what I can guarantee is more
people will talk about

00:09:52.430 --> 00:09:54.080
and share your idea.

00:09:54.080 --> 00:09:56.800
A useful analogy here sort of
like a batting average.

00:09:56.800 --> 00:09:58.700
Can you guarantee you're going
to hit a home run every time?

00:09:58.700 --> 00:09:59.540
No.

00:09:59.540 --> 00:10:01.300
But to the degree you can
improve your batting average,

00:10:01.300 --> 00:10:03.680
you're increasing the chance
that you get a hit each time.

00:10:03.680 --> 00:10:04.900
That's what these principles
can do.

00:10:04.900 --> 00:10:06.830
They can increase the chance
that people talk about and

00:10:06.830 --> 00:10:08.080
share your ideas.

00:10:08.080 --> 00:10:10.690
From 9 people to 10 people,
from-- if you think about a

00:10:10.690 --> 00:10:12.860
virality coefficient, the viral
coefficient, getting

00:10:12.860 --> 00:10:14.780
that number up above 1.

00:10:14.780 --> 00:10:16.400
And so what I'm going to talk
about is how to craft

00:10:16.400 --> 00:10:17.930
contagious content.

00:10:17.930 --> 00:10:20.330
By content, I both mean the
messages we wrap around our

00:10:20.330 --> 00:10:22.930
products, but also how we build
the products themselves

00:10:22.930 --> 00:10:24.240
for viral growth.

00:10:24.240 --> 00:10:26.040
Thinking how to make the
products more talkable and

00:10:26.040 --> 00:10:28.440
shareable and how we design both
websites, as well as the

00:10:28.440 --> 00:10:31.850
product themselves, to be
something people will pass on.

00:10:31.850 --> 00:10:34.550
By contagious, I mean that old
idea of spreading from person

00:10:34.550 --> 00:10:36.470
to person, just like
a virus might.

00:10:36.470 --> 00:10:38.550
But the first idea here is
actually the most important

00:10:38.550 --> 00:10:41.430
one, the first word, and
that is the word craft.

00:10:41.430 --> 00:10:43.450
So you might think that you can
