00:10:57.970 --> 00:10:58.920
But you might say, hold on.

00:10:58.920 --> 00:11:01.220
I'm working on a product
that not that exciting.

00:11:01.220 --> 00:11:03.270
So I do exec ad sessions
sometimes where someone will,

00:11:03.270 --> 00:11:06.330
say I sell cement.

00:11:06.330 --> 00:11:09.320
How can I make people talk
about and share cement?

00:11:09.320 --> 00:11:11.320
And what I'm going to talk about
is how these same ideas

00:11:11.320 --> 00:11:15.140
can be used to sell cement,
toilet paper, network

00:11:15.140 --> 00:11:16.300
software, whatever you want.

00:11:16.300 --> 00:11:18.890
Pick your most boring product,
by following these principles

00:11:18.890 --> 00:11:21.820
you can craft that product or
that idea to make it more

00:11:21.820 --> 00:11:23.670
talkable or shareable.

00:11:23.670 --> 00:11:25.090
And finally, the last
thing I want to say

00:11:25.090 --> 00:11:27.010
here is quite important.

00:11:27.010 --> 00:11:29.400
We're going focus in our next
few minutes that we have left

00:11:29.400 --> 00:11:31.560
