00:13:35.370 --> 00:13:39.130
So imagine you're down in the
Village one weekend, maybe

00:13:39.130 --> 00:13:40.275
it's this weekend.

00:13:40.275 --> 00:13:41.490
It's Saturday afternoon.

00:13:41.490 --> 00:13:43.110
You're looking for something to
eat, you're hungry, you're

00:13:43.110 --> 00:13:45.300
hanging out with your friends,
when you notice a hot dog

00:13:45.300 --> 00:13:46.230
restaurant.

00:13:46.230 --> 00:13:47.330
It seems pretty cool.

00:13:47.330 --> 00:13:48.150
You like hot dogs.

00:13:48.150 --> 00:13:51.870
You walk downstairs inside to
this place called Crif Dogs, a

00:13:51.870 --> 00:13:55.150
