there's nothing in the

00:19:39.520 --> 00:19:42.110
environment to remind us that
the product exists.

00:19:42.110 --> 00:19:44.020
So when people come back,
they talk about a lot.

00:19:44.020 --> 00:19:46.090
But they don't keep talking
about it because there's no

00:19:46.090 --> 00:19:47.850
trigger to remind them of
them of the product.

