00:21:56.120 --> 00:21:59.640
But if you think about it, why
is $100 cheesesteak good for

00:21:59.640 --> 00:22:01.520
Philly in terms of triggers.

00:22:01.520 --> 00:22:02.850
Because Philly has a
lot of cheesesteak.

00:22:02.850 --> 00:22:05.220
So every time you think of a
cheesesteak, you might think

00:22:05.220 --> 00:22:07.350
about this remarkable
cheesesteak.

00:22:07.350 --> 00:22:09.450
Whereas a $100 cheesesteak is
now so good for a restaurant

00:22:09.450 --> 00:22:10.280
in New York.

00:22:10.280 --> 00:22:12.880
Because you don't think about
cheesesteaks very often here.

00:22:12.880 --> 00:22:15.080
And so depending on what
environment you live in, what

00:22:15.080 --> 00:22:17.610
you see, what you hear, what
you smell is different.

00:22:17.610 --> 00:22:19.980
Women may have certain cues
that men don't have.

00:22:19.980 --> 00:22:22.530
Older people have certain cues
the young people don't have.

00:22:22.530 --> 00:22:24.160
Think about the environment
that people live in, it is

00:22:24.160 --> 00:22:26.290
important to think about the
right triggers to link our

00:22:26.290 --> 00:22:27.460
product to.

00:22:27.460 --> 00:22:29.960
And then the second thing is
just growing your habitat.

00:22:29.960 --> 00:22:33.370
So just like animals have a
habitat, a set of things in

00:22:33.370 --> 00:22:35.960
the environment they need to
survive, so deer have, they

00:22:35.960 --> 00:22:37.790
need water and certain
things to eat.

00:22:37.790 --> 00:22:40.840
Ideas have a habitat, a set of
cues or triggers that make

00:22:40.840 --> 00:22:42.280
people think about them.

00:22:42.280 --> 00:22:44.110
And so Kit Kat did a
really good job of

00:22:44.110 --> 00:22:45.455
growing their habitat.

00:22:45.455 --> 00:22:47.750
So you might say Kit Kat,
I really like those.

00:22:47.750 --> 00:22:49.750
But they were having a problem
a few years ago when no one

00:22:49.750 --> 00:22:50.830
would think about
their product.

00:22:50.830 --> 00:22:53.610
Everyone loved it, but they'd
