00:25:37.120 --> 00:25:39.220
Because we like to imitate
others, we often imitate

00:25:39.220 --> 00:25:41.720
others, but we can't imitate
them if we can't see them.

00:25:41.720 --> 00:25:43.770
So we talk a lot about making
things public and different

00:25:43.770 --> 00:25:45.620
ways to do that.

00:25:45.620 --> 00:25:48.090
Practical value is just news you
can use, basically useful

00:25:48.090 --> 00:25:49.940
