00:25:49.940 --> 00:25:54.010
And finally, stories build on
this idea of a Trojan horse.

00:25:54.010 --> 00:25:56.190
Basically almost all stories
are Trojan horses.

00:25:56.190 --> 00:25:59.750
They carry information, brands,
benefits inside

00:25:59.750 --> 00:26:01.580
